trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan arves.

trans-unit.source: The ClientTargetCollection type allows access to the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget> elements of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetSection> section element collection.
trans-unit.target: Typen ClientTargetCollection gir tilgang til den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget>elementer i den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetSection>delen element-samlingen.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetSection> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget>

trans-unit.source: It belongs to a group that includes <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget> and <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetSection>.
trans-unit.target: Den tilhører en gruppe som inneholder <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget>og <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetSection>.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetSection> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The ClientTargetCollection constructor is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren ClientTargetCollection skal ikke brukes direkte fra koden.

trans-unit.source: It is called by the ASP.NET configuration system.
trans-unit.target: Kalles av ASP.NET Konfigurasjonssystemet.

trans-unit.source: You obtain an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetCollection> class by using the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetSection.ClientTargets%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Du hente en forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetCollection>klassen ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetSection.ClientTargets%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetSection.ClientTargets%2A> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetCollection>

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget"></xref> object to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Legger til den angitte <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget"> </xref> objektet i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Before adding a client target to the collection, you must create a <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget> object and initialize its <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget.Alias%2A> and <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget.UserAgent%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Før du legger til en klientmål i samlingen, må du opprette en <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget>objekt og initialisere de <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget.Alias%2A>og <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget.UserAgent%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget.UserAgent%2A> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget.Alias%2A> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget"></xref> to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget"> </xref> å legge til i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Returns an array of the keys for all the configuration elements contained in the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en matrise av nøklene for alle konfigurasjonen elementene i den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetCollection"> </xref> samling.

trans-unit.source: The array of the keys for all of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget"></xref> objects contained in the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Matrisen av nøklene for alle de <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget"> </xref> objekter i den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Removes all the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget"></xref> objects from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner alle de <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ClientTarget"> </xref> objekter fra samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The result of updating the configuration file after calling the Clear method is dependent upon the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode> value chosen.
trans-unit.target: Resultatet av å oppdatere konfigurasjonsfilen når Fjern metoden er avhengig av den <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode>verdi valgte.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode>

trans-unit.source: To update the configuration file you use one of these two methods: <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Save%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Save%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Du bruker en av disse to måter for å oppdatere konfigurasjonsfilen: <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Save%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Save%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Save%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Save%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Calling <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Save%2A?displayProperty=fullName> is equivalent to calling <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Save%2A> when the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode> value is modified.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Kaller <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Save%2A?displayProperty=fullName>tilsvarer kaller <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Save%2A>når den <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode>verdien endres.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode> </xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Save%2A> </xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Save%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If you use the <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Save%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method, the following conditions apply: - If you pass the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode> or <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode> parameter value, then a `clear` element is inserted into the `clientTarget` section of the configuration file at the current hierarchy level.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du bruker den <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Save%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden, betingelsene nedenfor gjelder: – Hvis du sender den <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode>eller <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode>parameterverdien, og deretter en `clear` elementet er satt inn i den `clientTarget` delen av konfigurasjonsfilen på dette hierarkinivået.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode> </xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode> </xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Save%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - If you pass the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode> parameter value, a series of `remove` elements are added to the `clientTarget` section of the configuration file at the current hierarchy level.
trans-unit.target: -Hvis du sender den <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode>parameterverdi, en rekke `remove` elementer er lagt til i `clientTarget` delen av konfigurasjonsfilen på dette hierarkinivået.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode>

trans-unit.source: This removes all references to the `add` elements defined in the parent configuration files at higher levels in the hierarchy.
trans-unit.target: Dette fjerner alle referanser til den `add` elementer som er definert i de overordnede konfigurasjonsfilene i høye nivåer i hierarkiet.

trans-unit.source: With the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode> enumeration value, one additional property on the collection affects what gets serialized to the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Med den <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode>opplistingsverdien en ekstra på samlingen påvirker hva henter serialisert i konfigurasjonsfilen.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSaveMode>

trans-unit.source: The property is <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElementCollection.EmitClear%2A> and is `false` by default.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElementCollection.EmitClear%2A>og `false` som standard.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElementCollection.EmitClear%2A>

trans-unit.source: One of the following conditions applies: - When <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElementCollection.EmitClear%2A> is set to `true`, a `clear` element is inserted into the `clientTarget` section of the configuration file at the current hierarchy level.
trans-unit.target: En av de følgende betingelsene gjelder: – når <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElementCollection.EmitClear%2A>er satt til `true`, en `clear` elementet er satt inn i den `clientTarget` delen av konfigurasjonsfilen på dette hierarkinivået.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElementCollection.EmitClear%2A>

trans-unit.source: This removes all references to the `add` elements defined in the parent configuration files at higher levels in the hierarchy.
trans-unit.target: Dette fjerner alle referanser til den `add` elementer som er definert i de overordnede konfigurasjonsfilene i høye nivåer i hierarkiet.

trans-unit.source: - When <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElementCollection.EmitClear%2A> is set to `false`, the `clear` element is removed from the `clientTarget` section of the configuration file at the current hierarchy level, if it exists.
trans-unit.target: -Når <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElementCollection.EmitClear%2A>er satt til `false`, `clear` elementet fjernes fra den `clientTarget` delen av konfigurasjonsfilen på gjeldende hierarkinivå, hvis den finnes.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElementCollection.EmitClear%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Clear method actually deletes the `add` elements defined in the `clientTarget` section of the configuration file at the current hierarchy level.
trans-unit.target: Fjern for faktisk sletter den `add` elementer som er definert i den `clientTarget` delen av konfigurasjonsfilen på dette hierarkinivået.

trans-unit.source: It also removes all references to the `add` elements defined in the parent configuration files at higher levels in the hierarchy.
trans-unit.target: Alle referanser til fjernes også den `add` elementer som er definert i de overordnede konfigurasjonsfilene i høye nivåer i hierarkiet.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The `add` elements are not deleted from the `clientTarget` section of the parent configuration files.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den `add` elementer slettes ikke fra den `clientTarget` delen av konfigurasjonsfiler overordnede.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ClientTargetCollection.Remove%2A> method deletes the `add` element in the `clientTarget` section at the current hierarchy level and inserts a `remove` element.
